OL,3,C'No 10 North is open for business': PM
OL,4,Cto host first meeting in northern base
OL,6,FAndy Burnham said Whitehall's
OL,7,Fresistance to devolution is "over for
OL,8,Fgood" ahead of his first meeting at
OL,9,Fthe newly opened No 10 North in
OL,10,FManchester.
OL,12,FThe prime minister will work from his
OL,13,Fnew office on Friday, marking what he
OL,14,Fcalls "a new era of power flowing out
OL,15,Fof Whitehall and into every postcode".
OL,17,F"For 40 years, power and resources
OL,18,Fhave been sucked into the centre, and
OL,19,Ftoo many communities have felt
OL,20,Fforgotten, without the attention and
OL,21,Finvestment they deserve," Burnham said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
