FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784890079
OL,3,C'No 10 North is open for business': PM
OL,4,Cto host first meeting in northern base
OL,6,F"No 10 North will change that by
OL,7,Fputting more power into every postcode
OL,8,Facross the entire country. The days of
OL,9,FWhitehall resisting devolution are
OL,10,Fover, for good."
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
