OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784890079
OL,3,C'No 10 North is open for business': PM
OL,4,Cto host first meeting in northern base
OL,6,FThe new northern office is based in
OL,7,FHeron House in Manchester's city
OL,8,Fcentre and brings what the government
OL,9,Fdescribes as "the levers of local
OL,10,Feconomic growth and devolution
OL,11,Ftogether under one roof for the first
OL,12,Ftime".
OL,14,FBurnham is planning to work from this
OL,15,Fbureau at least one day every week to
OL,16,Fensure that decisions about the UK's
OL,17,Feconomic future will no longer be
OL,18,Fexclusively made in Westminster.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784890079
OL,3,C'No 10 North is open for business': PM
OL,4,Cto host first meeting in northern base
OL,6,FIt is expected that other ministers
OL,7,Fwill also work from the northern base
OL,8,Fon a regular basis, "underlining the
OL,9,Fgovernment's determination to do
OL,10,Fthings differently".
OL,12,FThe PM will also chair the first
OL,13,Fmeeting of the revived National
OL,14,FEconomic Council at the office on
OL,15,FFriday, bringing together government
OL,16,Fand regional mayors to put "devolution
OL,17,Fat the centre" of the government's
OL,18,Fplans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
