CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784890079
OL,3,C'No 10 North is open for business': PM
OL,4,Cto host first meeting in northern base
OL,6,FThe National Economic Council (NEC)
OL,7,Fwas established in 2008 to provide a
OL,8,Fjoined up response to the "economic
OL,9,Femergency".
OL,11,FIts revival, the government claims,
OL,12,Fnow reflects the PM's belief that the
OL,13,Fissue now requires the same "urgency,
OL,14,Ffocus and collective action".
OL,16,FBefore the meeting, Burnham will speak
OL,17,Fto business organisations including
OL,18,Fthe Federation of Small Businesses
OL,19,Fabout how they can work together to
OL,20,Fimprove growth, investment and the job
OL,21,Fmarket across the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
