SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784890079
OL,3,C'No 10 North is open for business': PM
OL,4,Cto host first meeting in northern base
OL,6,FFirst Secretary of State Louise Haigh
OL,7,Fsaid: "Today marks a fundamental re-
OL,8,Fbalancing of where power sits in our
OL,9,Fcountry.
OL,11,F"No 10 North has been set up to drive
OL,12,Feconomic growth in every postcode and
OL,13,Fput power in the hands of every
OL,14,Fcommunity.
OL,16,F"Through this department, this
OL,17,FGovernment will ensure that the places
OL,18,Foverlooked by Westminster for decades
OL,19,Fare given a real voice. No 10 North is
OL,20,Fopen for business."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
