CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784890079
OL,3,C'No 10 North is open for business': PM
OL,4,Cto host first meeting in northern base
OL,6,FBurnham originally proposed this move
OL,7,Fwhen he announced his run for Labour
OL,8,Fleadership, where he was then
OL,9,Funcontested.
OL,11,FThis announcement marks the end of the
OL,12,Ffirst working week for Burnham as
OL,13,Fprime minister, where he has announced
OL,14,Fpolicies to mark the start of this
OL,15,F"cost-of-living" government.
OL,17,FOn Tuesday, Burnham announced he would
OL,18,Fcut VAT on electricity bills from
OL,19,FOctober from 5% to 0% for six months,
OL,20,Fsaving the average household #45 over
OL,21,Fthat period.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
