PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1784890079
OL,3,C'No 10 North is open for business': PM
OL,4,Cto host first meeting in northern base
OL,6,FHe also said he is bringing back the
OL,7,F#2 cap on bus fares for England,
OL,8,Fexcluding London, in January, a policy
OL,9,Fthat mirrors his work in Manchester,
OL,10,Fwhere single fares already have the
OL,11,Fcap.
OL,13,FOn Thursday he pledged a 20% cut on
OL,14,Fbusiness rates for pubs, clubs and
OL,15,Fmusic venues from April next year, and
OL,16,Fsaid "pubs need to know the calvary is
OL,17,Fcoming".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
